Brief installation instructions as of 2005-02-17
- make a directory otf/ in the MinionPro directory
- copy all files with extension .otf into it.
- run ./scripts/makeall
- run ./scripts/install to copy the files to the localtexmf tree
                        or specify the target directory as parameter

You need the following programmes:
- cfftot1, otftotfm (Part of LCDF tools, http://www.lcdf.org/~eddietwo/type/).
  You need at least v2.25 or higher
- fontinst v1.925 or higher
